@startuml
!include _theme.puml
left to right direction

title Monitor — C4 System Context
caption Level 1: people, external systems, and the Monitor software system boundary

actor "Operations Analyst\nUses the live dashboard" as OpsUser
actor "On-call Engineer\nResponds to CRITICAL alerts" as OnCall

rectangle "Monitor System\nReal-time operations monitoring dashboard" as Monitor {
  component "Monitor Backend + Frontend\nSSE-based monitoring workflow" as MonitorSystem
}

database "Oracle XE / source database\nLOG_TRAZA changes" as Oracle
queue "Kafka\nCDC topic transport" as Kafka
component "Debezium / Kafka Connect\nCDC extraction" as Debezium
cloud "SMTP / Groupwise" as SMTP

OpsUser --> MonitorSystem : Views infrastructure and data events
OnCall <-- SMTP : Receives CRITICAL alert emails
OnCall --> MonitorSystem : Opens dashboard during incidents

Oracle --> Debezium : Database changes
Debezium --> Kafka : Debezium envelopes
Kafka --> MonitorSystem : CDC events consumed by backend
MonitorSystem --> SMTP : Async CRITICAL notifications

note right of MonitorSystem
Primary responsibilities:
- expose SSE stream to browser clients
- unify CDC and polling events
- push CRITICAL alerts to email
- keep SSE connections alive with heartbeats
end note
@enduml

